quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  4,60,"“Kodi sukuwaona omwe akungonena chabe kuti akhulupirira zomwe zavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe ndi zomwe zidavumbulutsidwa patsogolo pako, pomwe iwo akufuna kuti akaweruzidwe ndi maweruzo osagwirizana ndi Shariya, pomwenso alamulidwa kukana njira zotere? Koma satana akufuna kuwasokeretsa, kusokera kwakutali"
  4,61,"“Ndipo akauzidwa: “Idzani ku zomwe Allah wavumbulutsa, ndiponso (idzani) kwa Mtumiki.” Uwaona achinyengo akudziika kutali kwabasi ndi iwe"
  4,62,"“Kodi zingakhale bwanji litawabwerera vuto chifukwa cha zomwe manja awo adatsogoza? Kenako nkukudzera (iwe Mtumiki) uku akulumbira: “Tikulumbira Allah; sitinafune china chilichonse koma zabwino zokha ndi chimvano.”"
  4,63,"“Iwo ndi omwe Allah akudziwa zomwe zili m’mitima mwawo. Choncho dzipatule kwa iwo, ndipo alangize ndi kuwauza mawu ogwira mtima"
  4,64,"“Ndipo sitidamtumize mtumiki aliyense koma kuti azimveredwa mwa lamulo la Allah. Ngati akadakudzera pamene adadzichitira okha zoipa, (chifukwa chokafuna chiweruzo cha satana) napempha chikhululuko kwa Allah (naye) Mtumiki nkuwapempheranso chikhululuko, ndithudi, akadampeza Allah ali Wolandira kulapa kwawo ali Wachisoni chosatha"
  4,65,"“Ndikulumbira (m’choonadi cha) Mbuye wako, iwo sangakhale okhulupirira moona pokhapokha akuyese muweruzi wawo pa zomwe akukangana pakati pawo. Kenako asaone vuto m’mitima yawo pa zomwe waweruza, ndipo adzipereke kwathunthu (pogonjera chiweruzo chako)"